         <div type="translation" xml:lang="eng">
             <p rend="stanza" n="1-5">
Health! On the day of the bright half of the month that is the full moon day <supplied reason="explanation">i.e. the 15th day</supplied> of the Vaiśākha month in <foreign>saṃvat</foreign> 469, during King Rāmadeva's <supplied reason="explanation">reign of</supplied> more than a hundred years, the venerable Mahārāja Mahāsāmanta Kramalīla, being healthy, authorizes that Mānamatī has given land in Śālagaṃbī in the area of Dova village, with a produce of 28 <foreign>mānika</foreign> to Lord Nātheśvara, and [a further land-grant] in the same area yielding 2 <foreign>mānika</foreign> to <foreign>khuḍusvāmin</foreign>.
</p>
